KUTHIWA akasondele ophethe ithikithi elawina uR20 million we-lotto angaze aphelelwe isikhathi. Lokhu kuvezwe yiThuba okuyinkampani elawula iNational lottery ngesikhathi inxusa bonke abanamathikithi ukuba bawahlolisise. Bathi ithikithi elawina uR20 569,105 kwilotto yangomhla ka 29 Meyi lalithengwe eCarletonville eGauteng. Umnikazi walo wazikhethela yena izinombolo zakhe futhi wadlala ngo-R40. “Le mali izophelelwa isikhathi ngomhla ka 29 Meyi kulo nyaka,” kusho uCharmaine Mabuza oyi-CEO yeThuba. 